data.value:
Press B: Toggles Fly On/OFF Press Number 4: Respawns you Press T: Teleports to cursor
Note: You have to be Host in order to use the exploits. Freefall (Drops everyone through the floor) Crash World (Lags everyones' games until they die) Unlock All (Unlocks all achievements) Spoof Rank (Makes your rank change rapidly) Spinbot (Makes you spin in a circle)
